        {
            "title": "美加對貿易談判進展各執一詞 卡尼稱等美國準備好後可恢復磋商",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 在川普宣布中止與加拿大談判後，加拿大總理馬克·卡尼表示，當美國準備恢復談判時，加方做好重新開啟貿易磋商的準備。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「我們無法左右美國的貿易政策，」卡尼周五在登上政府專機、開啟為期九天的亞洲訪問行程前表示。「我們認識到，美國的貿易政策立場較上世紀八九十年代和本世紀初有了根本性變化。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">卡尼表示，加美雙方在鋼、鋁、能源等領域的談判已有進展。「一旦美方準備重啟談判，我們也準備在此前成果的基礎上繼續推進。」</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-8560687c-7f30-33cb-bc03-9a9f8bca125b-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">卡尼當天未接受記者提問。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">川普周四晚在社交媒體平台Truth Social上發文稱將終止與加拿大的一切談判，理由是一則由安大略省資助、並在電視上播放的廣告。這則廣告引用了前美國總統里根1987年的講話片段，其維護自由貿易、抨擊關稅制度「過時」。川普稱該廣告是「假的」，但廣告中使用的視頻片段是真實的。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">安大略省省長道格·福特周五早間似乎仍然支持該廣告。他在社交媒體上表示：「加拿大和美國是朋友、鄰居和盟友。里根總統知道，我們團結才能更強大。願上帝保佑加拿大，保佑美利堅。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">白宮高級顧問凱文·哈塞特對談判表達了不同看法。他在接受福克斯新聞採訪時表示,「事實上，與加拿大的談判並不友好，進展也不順利，我認為總統對此非常沮喪。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">由於去年約四分之三的出口商品流向美國，加拿大經濟在川普加徵關稅後遭受重創。擁有約1600萬人口的安大略省因其發達的鋼鐵和汽車產業而成為這場貿易戰的中心，而這正是川普重點徵稅的兩個行業。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">預計川普和卡尼將在下周碰面，兩人將分別出席在馬來西亞和韓國舉行的東協與亞太經合組織(APEC)峰會。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Carney Says Trade Talks Were Making Progress Before Trump Blowup</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Catherine Lucey、Mario Baker Ramirez.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%BE%8E%E5%8A%A0%E5%B0%8D%E8%B2%BF%E6%98%93%E8%AB%87%E5%88%A4%E9%80%B2%E5%B1%95%E5%90%84%E5%9F%B7-%E8%A9%9E-%E5%8D%A1%E5%B0%BC%E7%A8%B1%E7%AD%89%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E6%BA%96%E5%82%99%E5%A5%BD%E5%BE%8C%E5%8F%AF%E6%81%A2%E5%BE%A9%E7%A3%8B%E5%95%86-160649061.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-10-25 00:45:52",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "美國企業活動擴張速度創下今年次高水平 得益於訂單成長強勁",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 受訂單強勁成長推動，美國10月企業活動擴張速度創下今年以來第二高。為刺激銷售，企業在定價方面更加克制。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">標普全球周五公佈的數據顯示，10月綜合產出指數初值上漲近1點，至54.8。該指數高於50表明經濟活動處於擴張區間。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">新訂單綜合指標升至54.2，為今年以來最高水平。訂單成長主要受到製造業訂單量創去年2月以來最強勁增幅推動。服務業方面，新業務擴張也創下2024年底以來最大成長。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「數據表明第四季度開局經濟成長持續強勁，製造業與服務業的商業活動均呈現出加速勢頭，」標普全球市場情報的首席商業經濟學家Chris Williamson在聲明中表示。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-c800e3dd-03ac-3c0f-915f-d8361efa60b3-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">不過，調查報告的細分數據呈現出更多分化跡象。雖然工廠產出成長有所加快，但製造業就業指標降至三個月低點。服務業就業成長僅略快於前月。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">本月衡量原物料支付價格的綜合指標小幅上升，但仍維持在60.8的高位；相比之下，銷售價格指標增速為六個月以來最慢，Williamson指出，這表明企業正在通過價格競爭來爭取訂單。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">與此同時，訂單積壓情況基本停滯，出口新訂單出現六個月來最大降幅，這與企業更積極的降價策略相一致。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題US Business Activity Expands at Second-Fastest Pace This Year</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E4%BC%81%E6%A5%AD%E6%B4%BB%E5%8B%95%E6%93%B4%E5%BC%B5%E9%80%9F%E5%BA%A6%E5%89%B5%E4%B8%8B%E4%BB%8A%E5%B9%B4%E6%AC%A1%E9%AB%98%E6%B0%B4%E5%B9%B3-%E5%BE%97%E7%9B%8A%E6%96%BC%E8%A8%82%E5%96%AE%E6%88%90%E9%95%B7%E5%BC%B7%E5%8B%81-143408758.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-10-24 23:25:52",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "通用汽車裁員逾200人 降本增效應對關稅逆風",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> <a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:通用汽車;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/通用汽車\">通用汽車</a>周五裁減數百個崗位，就在幾日前該公司上調全年利潤指引推動股價大漲。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">據知情人士透露，通用汽車解雇了超過200名受薪員工，主要集中在密西根州沃倫市的技術中心。因討論未公開信息而要求匿名的知情人士表示，消息於上午7點左右傳達，公司通過Slack頻道通知部分受影響員工，稱此次裁員出於「業務狀況」考慮，與個人業績無關。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在汽車製造商努力應對美國總統川普不斷變化的政策之際，通用汽車一直在精簡架構以提高利潤。儘管關稅推高了成本，但車企大多未能通過提價來抵消。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-410fdaea-6cd4-3c46-a29b-a364e8679ffe-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">通用汽車在本周早些時候公佈了優於預期的第三季度財報，推動公司股價錄得逾五年來最大單日漲幅。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題GM Cuts Hundreds of Salaried Workers as Part of Profit Push (1)</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%80%9A%E7%94%A8%E6%B1%BD%E8%BB%8A%E8%A3%81%E5%93%A1%E9%80%BE200%E4%BA%BA-%E9%99%8D%E6%9C%AC%E5%A2%9E%E6%95%88%E6%87%89%E5%B0%8D%E9%97%9C%E7%A8%85%E9%80%86%E9%A2%A8-140318973.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-10-24 22:55:56",
