        {
            "title": "印度據悉接近與美國敲定貿易協議 但強調不會倉促簽署",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"10月24日，Piyush Goyal在柏林\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/kaThwvotaSheRAf7294ECA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/5243b7a2461abf6d55bcbef8a208a180\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">10月24日，Piyush Goyal在柏林</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 一位政府官員表示，印度接近與美國敲定貿易協定，雙方在大多數議題上接近達成一致。儘管印度商務部長強調，新德里不會倉促簽署任何協議。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">因討論未公開消息而要求匿名的知情官員表示，大多數問題已趨於一致，雙方達成協議在望。而印度商務部長Piyush Goyal早些時候稱，印度不會迫於壓力達成協議。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"10月24日，Piyush Goyal在柏林Photographer: Krisztian Bocsi/Bloomberg\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/WZJaTX7faE8mZRY4HBjIbQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/5fb4ff81e32457b31a618ebef5207d51\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">10月24日，Piyush Goyal在柏林Photographer: Krisztian Bocsi/Bloomberg</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「我們不會倉促達成交易，也不會在最後期限或壓力下達成交易，」Goyal在德國柏林出席活動時表示。「我們已經接受，如果要對我們徵收關稅，那就征吧。」</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-52040026-7820-39c8-be49-64735d2cbe95-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美國總統唐納德·川普以印度購買俄羅斯石油且不願擴大美國產品市場准入為由，對印度實施了50%的懲罰性關稅。華盛頓方面要求新德里停止所有俄羅斯進口，這是達成貿易協議的關鍵條件。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這位知情官員表示，雙方談判代表通過線上會議就協議的法律用語進行磋商，最終決定需由兩國領導層作出。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題India Signals US Trade Deal Even as Minister Says It Won’t Rush</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Savio Shetty.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%8D%B0%E5%BA%A6%E6%93%9A%E6%82%89%E6%8E%A5%E8%BF%91%E8%88%87%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E6%95%B2%E5%AE%9A%E8%B2%BF%E6%98%93%E5%8D%94%E8%AD%B0-%E4%BD%86%E5%BC%B7%E8%AA%BF%E4%B8%8D%E6%9C%83%E5%80%89%E4%BF%83%E7%B0%BD%E7%BD%B2-122626594.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-10-24 21:05:47",
