        {
            "title": "前瑞銀董事長Weber警告：人工智能將催生新貴階層 同時加劇就業不平等",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"Axel Weber，前德國央行行長、前瑞銀集團董事長。攝影師：Aaron Schwartz/ 彭博\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/foQcjdTkenWxaKIoqW_e6g--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/571134c7e1fed3a90bb5060857c4b739\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">Axel Weber，前德國央行行長、前瑞銀集團董事長。攝影師：Aaron Schwartz/ 彭博</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">【彭博】— 前瑞銀集團董事長Axel Weber警告稱，<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:人工智能;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/人工智能\">人工智能</a>即將帶來顛覆性變革，可能會催生新的全球精英階層，他們將從這項尖端技術的應用中收獲不成比例的收益，而其他人則會陷入更糟糕的處境。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「我們將看到人們以前所未見的方式從這項新技術中攫取利益。」也曾擔任德國央行掌門人的Weber周五在上海外灘年會的專題小組討論中表示：「類似於科技貴族及億萬富翁曾經的崛起，我們將目睹一個人工智能貴族階層的誕生。」</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-f8958495-e06c-3367-b067-92e5fc4a1b19-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">現年68歲的Weber擔心，人工智能技術可能導致大規模失業，在那些能夠與人工智能協作的人和其他面臨被取代風險的人之間，就業境遇之差可能有如天壤之別。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「影響將極其深遠，」他說，「但對於那些能駕馭人工智能浪潮、乘勢而上的群體來說，這將是一段精妙絕倫的旅程。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Ex-UBS Chairman Weber Warns AI Ushering In New Era of Inequality</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:1;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%89%8D%E7%91%9E%E9%8A%80%E8%91%A3%E4%BA%8B%E9%95%B7weber%E8%AD%A6%E5%91%8A-%E4%BA%BA%E5%B7%A5%E6%99%BA%E8%83%BD%E5%B0%87%E5%82%AC%E7%94%9F%E6%96%B0%E8%B2%B4%E9%9A%8E%E5%B1%A4-%E5%90%8C%E6%99%82%E5%8A%A0%E5%8A%87%E5%B0%B1%E6%A5%AD%E4%B8%8D%E5%B9%B3%E7%AD%89-092207058.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-10-24 19:55:45",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "特朗普稱與加拿大的所有貿易談判終止 加元下跌",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"特朗普稱與加拿大的所有貿易談判終止 加元下跌\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/028khb.CNDuxTIViS6qMpQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2025-10/b06b3560-b0c4-11f0-acbb-dcaea4092f6b\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">特朗普稱與加拿大的所有貿易談判終止 加元下跌</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%B7%9D%E6%99%AE%E7%A8%B1%E8%88%87%E5%8A%A0%E6%8B%BF%E5%A4%A7%E7%9A%84%E6%89%80%E6%9C%89%E8%B2%BF%E6%98%93%E8%AB%87%E5%88%A4%E7%B5%82%E6%AD%A2-%E5%8A%A0%E5%85%83%E4%B8%8B%E8%B7%8C-031136938.html",
